    <briefdescription>
<para>Matrix helper class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The matrix helper class provide the following fuctionality:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Getter function to retrieve the matrix inverse</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Functions to print a matrix or a vector</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Functions to initialize a matrix or a vector</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Function to set a value at defined indices</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Multiplication of matrix with vector</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Substraction of vectors</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Function to retrieve the matrix cofactors</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Function to retrieve the transposed matrix</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Function to retrieve the matrix determinant </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
